headline: Alight, Iridium, CDW, First Advantage, and Xerox Shares Are Soaring, What You Need To Know
summary: A number of stocks jumped in the afternoon session after the latest Personal Consumption Expenditures (PCE) Price Index report aligned with economists' predictions, signaling that inflation is under control.
